 />\n<br />\n4個人食左只係&yen;15xxx （9折 連税 有飲野）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8SCd9n8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8SCd9n8.png&h=f573864d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LT8T9oa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLT8T9oa.png&h=5b632e03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n附上9折卷 請慢用<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gcDtdSP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgcDtdSP.png&h=c961a83e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c496177d1a173e96355cfbc76745c6236658839c","tid":950070,"uid":101481,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T12:11:39.000Z","msg":"万両"},{"pid":"ea5c974b2834afc555bc4b47d2fdae649a50d0f3","tid":950070,"uid":205844,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T12:14:50.000Z","msg":"力丸真心垃撚圾喎，全撚部都係得香港人大陸人台灣人食，伏撚到爆，又唔係平"},{"pid":"067d0ec9a8842b74bf26e21a8d41da66be787535","tid":950070,"uid":84159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ea5c974b2834afc555bc4b47d2fdae649a50d0f3","tid":950070,"uid":205844,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T12:14:50.000Z","msg":"力丸真心垃撚圾喎，全撚部都係得香港人大陸人台灣人食，伏撚到爆，又唔係平"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T12:19:07.000Z","msg":"我想問全撚部都係香港人大陸人台灣人 咁代表d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n即係有以上人食既就好撚垃圾啊？ 定其他意思？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n即係入到去冇依三種人就一定好唔伏？"},{"pid":"f63bd1755119592f3f113e13b4519f809c5d7c13","tid":950070,"uid":205844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"067d0ec9a8842b74bf26e21a8d41da66be787535","tid":950070,"uid":84159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ea5c974b2834afc555bc4b47d2fdae649a50d0f3","tid":950070,"uid":205844,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T12:14:50.000Z","msg":"力丸真心垃